@node Bugs "AnimIcon - Known Bugs "

@{b}Known Bugs@{ub}
**********

Currently the select image is taken from the original icon. If this is not
exactly the same size (width and height) as the animation then it gets
scrambled. This doesn't seem to happen if the icon only has old imagery ie.
no palletemapped image.

Also if the select image is transparent then the aniamtion is not erased
before drawing it. If the icon is moved slightly when selecting then the
animation image is deleted but otherwise it can still be seen..


If you find any please send a bug report or in fact any comments at all to
the @{"author" LINK Author}.

@endnode

